  allLines:
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1936918675910826544, guid: e8f1130d0e09cef45bb1f9ab49489848, type: 3}
    sentence: "Best not to get drunk around you then, \u2018cause desperation really
      isn\u2019t my thing. "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dc24e77c8220d5b43bd418e911809b3b, type: 3}
    sentence: I can tell. Well, everyone can get desperate if they want something
      badly enough.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1936918675910826544, guid: e8f1130d0e09cef45bb1f9ab49489848, type: 3}
    sentence: "And I definitely don\u2019t want you that bad. At least not yet."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dc24e77c8220d5b43bd418e911809b3b, type: 3}
    sentence: Not yet, yes.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Hate to interrupt, for a fun reason at least. I have a little game
      for the both of you to get to know each other better.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "The tablet in front of you displays the Icebreaker. A game I\u2019m
      sure both of you are familiar with, being good communicators and all!"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Niceeee, you\u2019re getting good at this."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
